## Summary

The User Privacy API enables programmatic deletion of user data (events and properties) for GDPR/CCPA compliance using Amplitude IDs or User IDs, with batch processing, scheduling delays up to 30 days, and organization-wide deletion capabilities via the `delete_from_org` parameter.

